  audioProfileName: 
  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Neither Master Impassive, nor Ser Invyncible, nor the Apprentice
      saw the circle.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Maybe I did get hit on the head too hard...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The dead being reanimated and rocks coming to life and attacking
      people seem quite abnormal.


      However, at least you can attack something
      you can see.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Who am I talking to?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'A tear in reality that no one can see though...


      That could
      end the world without anyone ever knowing there was a threat.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Is this some kind of internal monologue?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Now would be a good time to return to the Guardian of Souls.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Beam Me Up...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Perhaps it knows why no one else can see the tear and how to find
      the source and stop it.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Abra Cadabra? Hey, how does this thing work?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Use your Teleport Soul Forge ability to return to the Guardian Of
      Souls.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Up, Up, and Away...
  prerequisiteConditions: []
